---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  lang="en"
  title="Age Calculator | Sahloo سهلو"
  description="Free age calculator — find your exact age in years, months, days, and weeks from your birthdate."
  canonical="https://sahloo.com/en/tools/age-calculator/"
>
<main id="main" class="tool-page">
  <div class="tool-hero">
    <div class="container--n container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="breadcrumb"><a href="#" class="lang-switch">Home</a><span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><a href="/en/tools/">Tools</a><span class="bc-sep" aria-hidden="true">›</span><span aria-current="page">Age Calculator</span></nav>
<script type="application/ld+json">{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList", "itemListElement": [{"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://sahloo.com/en/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Tools", "item": "https://sahloo.com/en/tools/"}, {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Age Calculator"}]}</script>
      <div class="tool-hero-content">
        <div class="tool-page-icon" aria-hidden="true">🎂</div>
        <h1 class="tool-page-title">Age Calculator</h1>
        <p class="tool-page-sub">Find your exact age in years, months, and days</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container--n container" style="padding-top:24px;">
    <div class="calc-card">
      <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" for="bDate">Date of birth</label><input type="date" class="form-input" id="bDate" required></div>
      <div class="form-group"><label class="form-label" for="tDate">Calculate age as of</label><input type="date" class="form-input" id="tDate"><p class="form-hint">Leave blank for today</p></div>
      <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full" onclick="calcAge()">Calculate Age →</button>
      <div class="result-card" id="ageRes" aria-live="polite">
        <div class="result-label">Your age</div>
        <div class="result-grid">
          <div class="result-item"><div class="val" id="aY">0</div><div class="lbl">Year(s)</div></div>
          <div class="result-item"><div class="val" id="aM">0</div><div class="lbl">Month(s)</div></div>
          <div class="result-item"><div class="val" id="aD">0</div><div class="lbl">Day(s)</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="result-sub" id="aSub"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-section"><div class="info-card"><h2>🎂 About the Age Calculator</h2>
<p>This tool calculates your exact age based on your date of birth, giving you the result in years, months, days, total weeks, and total days.</p>
<p>It's useful for official documents, medical check-ins, job applications, or simply satisfying your curiosity!</p></div>
<div class="info-card"><h2>🧮 How to Use</h2>
<ol class="steps-list"><li>Enter your date of birth in the first field.</li><li>Optionally set a target date in the second field (defaults to today).</li><li>Click "Calculate Age" for instant results.</li></ol></div>
<div class="info-card"><h2>💡 Did You Know?</h2>
<ul><li>The average human lifespan is roughly <strong>28,000 days</strong>.</li>
<li>Leap years add an extra day every 4 years (roughly), affecting age calculations.</li>
<li>Some cultures count age from conception rather than birth.</li></ul></div><div class="info-card" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage"><h2>❓ FAQ</h2><div class="faq-list"><div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="fa0" itemprop="name">How is my exact age calculated?<span class="faq-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a" id="fa0" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><span itemprop="text">We subtract your birthdate from today (or the target date) using calendar-accurate arithmetic, accounting for leap years and different month lengths.</span></div></div>
<div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="fa1" itemprop="name">Can I calculate age as of a specific date?<span class="faq-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a" id="fa1" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><span itemprop="text">Yes — enter any target date in the second field to calculate your age as of that date.</span></div></div>
<div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="fa2" itemprop="name">Does the calculator support Hijri dates?<span class="faq-arrow" aria-hidden="true">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a" id="fa2" itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer"><span itemprop="text">The calculator uses the Gregorian calendar. For Hijri conversion, a separate calendar converter tool is recommended.</span></div></div>
</div></div>
</div>
  </div>
  <section class="related-section container--n container" aria-label="Related Tools"><div class="section-hd"><h2 class="section-title">Related Tools</h2><a href="/en/tools/" class="see-all">All Tools</a></div><div class="tools-grid"><a href="/en/tools/percentage-calculator/" class="tool-card"><div class="tool-icon" aria-hidden="true">📊</div><div class="tool-name">Percentage Calculator</div><div class="tool-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div></a><a href="/en/tools/zakat-calculator/" class="tool-card"><div class="tool-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌙</div><div class="tool-name">Zakat Calculator</div><div class="tool-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div></a><a href="/en/tools/currency-converter/" class="tool-card"><div class="tool-icon" aria-hidden="true">💱</div><div class="tool-name">Currency Converter</div><div class="tool-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div></a><a href="/en/tools/loan-calculator/" class="tool-card"><div class="tool-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏦</div><div class="tool-name">Loan Calculator</div><div class="tool-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div></a></div></section>
</main>

<script is:inline>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',()=>{document.getElementById('tDate').value=new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0];});
function calcAge(){
  const b=new Date(document.getElementById('bDate').value);
  const t=new Date(document.getElementById('tDate').value||new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]);
  if(!document.getElementById('bDate').value||b>t)return;
  let y=t.getFullYear()-b.getFullYear(),m=t.getMonth()-b.getMonth(),d=t.getDate()-b.getDate();
  if(d<0){m--;d+=new Date(t.getFullYear(),t.getMonth(),0).getDate();}
  if(m<0){y--;m+=12;}
  const td=Math.floor((t-b)/86400000);
  const fmt=n=>new Intl.NumberFormat('en-US').format(n);
  document.getElementById('aY').textContent=fmt(y);
  document.getElementById('aM').textContent=fmt(m);
  document.getElementById('aD').textContent=fmt(d);
  document.getElementById('aSub').textContent='Total: '+fmt(td)+' days | '+fmt(Math.floor(td/7))+' weeks';
  document.getElementById('ageRes').classList.add('show');
}
</script>

</Layout>
